{"tid":2116354,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]英短3個月大柯軟便","createTime":"2020-07-20T06:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T00:46:41.000Z","uid":194766,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ac2710e4da37185a66d264d4898b8dce22d0ff0a","tid":2116354,"uid":194766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T06:06:27.000Z","msg":"養左貓貓一個月，佢而家兩個月大<br />\nKeep住柯林既屎 每日兩三次<br />\n睇過兩次醫生 食過益生菌同抗生素 腸胃糧都食僅<br />\n杜蟲藥咩都試過<br />\n仍然冇靚屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食完腸胃糧D屎好左少少 唔係一pat野 係一條條似軟雪糕<br />\n但食慾正常 玩得跑得跳得 好活躍<br />\n而家拎左D屎去驗<br />\n請問有冇奴才有類似經驗？<br />\n好擔心貓貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aqy75C7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAqy75C7.png&h=cd88c660&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0c7f77b42d1f73b67f3b2f85386b4198599a248","tid":2116354,"uid":5944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"一日兩三次好似多咗啲<br />\n不過睇完醫生都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我嗰隻冇咁嚴重<br />\n但都試過睇咗兩次醫生都係軟屎<br />\n之後醫生開咗隻有益生菌嘅糧<br />\n食咗一兩日就冇事<br />\n<br />\n但你都可以睇下會唔會係屋企環境或者佢皮膚有菌<br />\n然後lam毛lam埋落肚"},{"pid":"ef23a6617d501e0f1f85011fc8b5bd3058645a54","tid":2116354,"uid":170025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac2710e4da37185a66d264d4898b8dce22d0ff0a","tid":2116354,"uid":194766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T06:06:27.000Z","msg":"養左貓貓一個月，佢而家兩個月大<br />\nKeep住柯林既屎 每日兩三次<br />\n睇過兩次醫生 食過益生菌同抗生素 腸胃糧都食僅<br />\n杜蟲藥咩都試過<br />\n仍然冇靚屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食完腸胃糧D屎好左少少 唔係一pat野 係一條條似軟雪糕<br />\n但食慾正常 玩得跑得跳得 好活躍<br />\n而家拎左D屎去驗<br />\n請問有冇奴才有類似經驗？<br />\n好擔心貓貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aqy75C7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAqy75C7.png&h=cd88c660&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T06:11:46.000Z","msg":"樓主可以試下喂寵物益生菌，自己果隻有時唔知點解柯肚(但玩得食得)食呢個有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2354d6f0c612515c43f8a8b2c878fa91d25e5af","tid":2116354,"uid":47826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T06:14:11.000Z","msg":"試下蒸雞柳 (超市果D)<br />\n食2-3餐 同埋餵益生菌"},{"pid":"8c485deea48675df45c4841cc5a9a2a13d34d782","tid":2116354,"uid":47826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T06:19:45.000Z","msg":"我有隻貓之前食咩乾糧都軟便<br />\n食罐就要試唔同<br />\n要keep 住搵邊隻無事<br />\n我罐NV 雞, Weruva Truluxe無事 <br />\nthrive, Ziwi, K9, wellness core 都軟便<br />\n乾糧永遠唔得<br />\n所以唯有試到邊隻好"},{"pid":"6e49e9eeb5f169afa92b3c63eedd8ebeb10f4311","tid":2116354,"uid":194766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c485deea48675df45c4841cc5a9a2a13d34d782","tid":2116354,"uid":47826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T06:19:45.000Z","msg":"我有隻貓之前食咩乾糧都軟便<br />\n食罐就要試唔同<br />\n要keep 住搵邊隻無事<br />\n我罐NV 雞, Weruva Truluxe無事 <br />\nthrive, Ziwi, K9, wellness core 都軟便<br />\n乾糧永遠唔得<br />\n所以唯有試到邊隻好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T06:42:14.000Z","msg":"試吓先！但唔食乾糧會唔會唔夠營養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03316f8c4a77a7f66c977501c9f856824018e89","tid":2116354,"uid":7507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T07:14:55.000Z","msg":"試下食幾日白烚雞胸肉 其他咩都唔好比佢食<br />\n<br />\n我個隻都長期軟便 痾水又有 帶血又有  去做body check<br />\n<br />\n驗埋屎個啲都冇發現  唯有都係食下雞胸肉先靚少少啲屎<br />\n<br />\n我個隻腸胃極敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866010bef0332fb845db7bc7e57083ad13618ddd","tid":2116354,"uid":194766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f03316f8c4a7